## packages/ Directory Details

### uv Workspace Structure

This project uses a **uv workspace** to manage multiple Python packages. The `packages/` directory contains two types of packages:

{#quick-reference-table}

| Package Name | Type | Description | uv Command Prefix |
|-------------|------|-------------|-------------------|
| `xeno-parser` | Workspace Member | PDF parsing and OCR tool for document processing | `--package xeno-parser` |
| `xeno-serve` | Non-member | Service deployment related | `--project packages/xeno-serve` |
| `xeno-nmt-core` | Non-member | Neural machine translation core | `--project packages/xeno-nmt-core` |
| `mineru-api` | Non-member | Mineru API | `--project mineru-api` |

